description:
So you're not going to believe this. I, tamers12345, was in the notre dame cathedral when it caught on fire. I was taking a dump when I heard an explosion. I LITERALLY thought it was a modern sonic fan who came to kill me LMAO. Good for him that it wasn't because you know I would have put up a hell of a fight with god above haha.

I heard the fire was an accident or some sh*t
